headline: Assessing Accenture (ACN) Valuation After New AI Acquisition And Digital Trust Partnership
summary: Accenture (ACN) is back in focus after a pair of AI centric moves: the planned acquisition of UK based AI firm Faculty and a new digital trust partnership with NTT DOCOMO GLOBAL. See our latest analysis for Accenture. The recent AI driven deals come after a choppy spell where a weaker outlook and caution around public sector demand weighed on sentiment.
